text: Collingswood is a borough in Camden County, New Jersey, United States.Locate Your Business Here!, Borough of Collingswood. Accessed September 18, 2017. "Nestled between the Benjamin Franklin and Walt Whitman Bridges 4 miles from Center City Philadelphia, Collingswood is one of the most convenient towns in southern New Jersey." As of the 2020 United States Census, the borough's population was 14,186. ==References== Category:Boroughs in New Jersey Category:Camden County, New Jersey
